rComments: Class was pretty easy, she can be picky at times but if you put in some effort. Great class, I learned a lot! And she's super sweet

Very interesting in lecture and keeps your attention. In lab she can be very picky about the designs and picks them apart if they don't match her examples. She starts the grading under 100 to leave room for "creativity points" that you hardly ever see. Overall a pretty good class though.

Dianne is GREAT!!!! She is one of the most entertaining professors I've ever had. She's very helpful in lab! You can tell how passionate she is about flowers! The book is not needed, but unless you have a friend in lecture to copy notes for you, you should probably go. You get to take home a floral arrangement every week! Highly recommended!
Seems fun at first but is extremely picky. Instructions and expectations aren't very clear.
